  <brief_title>Febuxostat-Controlled, Double-Blind, Comparative Study of FYU-981 in Hyperuricemia With or Without Gout</brief_title>
  <official_title>Febuxostat-Controlled, Double-Blind, Comparative Study of FYU-981 for Hyperuricemia With or Without Gout to Evaluate the Safety and Noninferiority of FYU-981 (Phase III Study)</official_title>
