  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      FYU-981 or Febuxostat are administrated to hyperuricemia patients (underexcretion and mixed
      types) with or without gout for 14 weeks to compare the efficacy and safety of these drugs by
      the method of multicenter, randomized, double-blind, ascending dose regimen.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
